8
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:19,050
Screw you.

9
00:00:19,820 --> 00:00:21,160
I must get out.

10
00:00:21,370 --> 00:00:22,510
Given the way I am now,

11
00:00:22,510 --> 00:00:23,550
who can stop me?

12
00:00:25,080 --> 00:00:25,670
Boss.

13
00:00:25,870 --> 00:00:26,540
Listen,

14
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:28,980
