24
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:44,570
Then take the fall.

25
00:00:44,690 --> 00:00:45,730
If you get replaced,

26
00:00:45,730 --> 00:00:47,330
I can just find someone else.

27
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:50,440
Wa,

28
00:00:51,020 --> 00:00:53,060
I finally got a proper job.

29
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:55,170
