30
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:01,020
A proper job?

31
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:03,830
How do you think you got in here?

32
00:01:05,940 --> 00:01:06,850
Listen.

33
00:01:07,310 --> 00:01:09,350
I'll talk to the guys at the workshop.

34
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:10,140
Starting next week,

35
00:01:10,140 --> 00:01:11,940
they'll give me some extra points.

36
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,670
And for the drama competition,

37
00:01:14,190 --> 00:01:15,810
only one group is participating.

38
00:01:15,810 --> 00:01:17,440
They're making me the director

39
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:19,039
so that I can get more points.

40
00:01:19,940 --> 00:01:22,690
Director,
I want you to take advantage of me.

41
00:01:24,140 --> 00:01:25,310
For medical parole

42
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:27,770
