I must qualify for both.

43
00:01:27,770 --> 00:01:29,020
Do you understand?

44
00:01:29,690 --> 00:01:32,190
Every second
I can spend with my son counts.

45
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,890
I almost forgot the most important thing.

46
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:39,520
Here.

47
00:01:40,020 --> 00:01:41,560
Which cells need cigarettes

48
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,440
and which ones need fried chicken are

49
