all clearly written on it.

50
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,190
Handle these things for me.

51
00:01:48,190 --> 00:01:49,850
I'll offer you a bigger bonus.

52
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:51,190
Let's say

53
00:01:51,190 --> 00:01:52,100
100,000.

54
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:55,650
Consider it your Mid-Autumn Festival gift.

55
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,390
Inmate 7392,

56
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:02,470
