104
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,810
Oh, so sweet.

105
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:18,770
What's this?

106
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:20,020
This is for you.

107
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,520
It's for you.

108
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,540
Here you go.

109
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:30,180
Your brother's keychain was
quite hard to find.

110
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:32,620
How did you find it?

111
00:05:34,170 --> 00:05:36,590
I went to Thailand...

112
00:05:36,620 --> 00:05:38,159
You went to Thailand?

113
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:41,570
No, I mean I bought it
from a Thai shopping platform.

114
00:05:41,810 --> 00:05:43,350
You scared me.

115
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:45,640
