all the way to Thailand for it.

116
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,690
That was clever.

117
00:05:47,110 --> 00:05:49,240
And it took him quite a while to find it.

118
00:05:49,420 --> 00:05:50,790
How do you know that?

119
00:05:50,890 --> 00:05:52,520
He used my computer.

120
00:05:53,770 --> 00:05:54,770
Thanks.

121
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:57,440
It looks the same, I guess.

122
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:03,640
Do you want some more?

123
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,230
Sure.

124
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:09,470
You don't seem to have finished yours.

125
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:11,020
Is it too hard?

126
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:12,550
No, I'm just

127
00:06:13,810 --> 00:06:14,690
savoring it.

128
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,540
Xiaohui, I've been waiting for ages.

129
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,190
Be patient.

130
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:26,320
What medication are you prescribing?

131
00:06:26,350 --> 00:06:27,480
I was coughing all night yesterday.

132
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,100
Nobody heard me, huh?

133
00:06:29,770 --> 00:06:31,370
I've been coughing for days.

134
00:06:32,690 --> 00:06:33,690
Do I have to cough myself to death
before anyone notices?

135
00:06:33,690 --> 00:06:35,820
Inmate 7692 says he's feeling unwell.

136
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:36,890
Keep it down.

137
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:38,190
Lie down on Bed No.1 first, okay?

138
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:39,020
Okay.

139
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,220
Always complaining.

140
00:06:40,770 --> 00:06:42,390
Alright, put your mask on.

141
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:44,020
It protects both you and me.

142
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:44,690
Can you make it?

143
00:06:44,690 --> 00:06:45,770
Yes.

144
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,040
Just a moment.

145
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:51,170
Alright, let me check
your blood pressure first.

146
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,690
Keep it down.

147
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,390
Don't infect me.

148
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,050
What symptoms are you having?

149
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:58,600
Director,

150
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:01,330
the planned expansion site is
that area outside.

151
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,560
Currently, we're planning
to build two new cell blocks

152
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,560
and one more workshop.

153
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,390
Counselor,

154
00:07:05,390 --> 00:07:06,140
could you please

155
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:08,270
take more frontal shots
of the Director's face

156
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:10,480
and capture more footage
of him instructing us?

157
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,560
Thanks, I appreciate it.

158
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,060
Hold on.

159
00:07:12,350 --> 00:07:14,950
But I can't control
the Director's movements.

160
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,010
Don't worry about that.

161
00:07:16,010 --> 00:07:17,670
The Director knows what to do.

162
00:07:17,690 --> 00:07:18,890
Thanks for your help.

163
00:07:20,690 --> 00:07:22,750
Try to finish as quickly as possible.

164
00:07:22,940 --> 00:07:23,810
Yijie.

165
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:28,620
The Custody Division will be short
of staff after the expansion.

166
00:07:30,230 --> 00:07:30,850
I know.

167
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,890
There's a vacant deputy chief position.

168
00:07:32,890 --> 00:07:33,480
Are you interested...

169
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,540
Sorry, Dad. I'm in the middle of work.

170
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,320
Watch out, Director!

171
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,810
Be careful! Are you alright, Director?

172
00:07:38,810 --> 00:07:39,730
What happened?

173
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:40,980
Director!

174
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:43,890
Your blood pressure is a bit high.

175
00:07:43,890 --> 00:07:46,140
When I'm not feeling okay,
I need to see you, babe.

176
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:48,520
Don't say this. You have a wife.

177
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,890
Why are you just like my beautiful wife?

178
00:07:49,890 --> 00:07:51,140
Such a jealous one.

179
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:53,270
This isn't right.

180
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:54,440
Relax.

181
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,270
Okay.

182
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:57,330
Seeing you just makes me feel better.

183
00:07:57,770 --> 00:07:59,140
Can you please stop coughing?

184
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:00,890
Damn you.

185
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:01,890
Xiaohui.

186
00:08:03,050 --> 00:08:04,910
Could you wait for me for a moment?

187
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:06,190
So you're here.

188
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,570
Didn't you hear the walkie-talkie?

189
00:08:08,570 --> 00:08:09,640
It's just busy today.

190
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,640
You deliberately brought the inmate here
to see Xiaohui, didn't you?

191
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,980
No, it was just a coincidence.

192
00:08:12,980 --> 00:08:14,020
What's wrong?

193
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:15,640
The visiting director is injured.

194
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,020
Could you go check on him?

195
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:18,080
I'm kind of busy.

196
00:08:18,110 --> 00:08:19,020
Do I have to go right now?

197
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:21,270
-There are no doctors on duty today.
-Yeah.

198
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:22,770
They've already called an ambulance.

199
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:24,390
But the Chief is making a fuss over there.

200
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:25,480
Just tell them to wait there

201
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,890
for the ambulance.

202
00:08:26,890 --> 00:08:27,890
It's just a fall.

203
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:28,890
You tell him that.

204
00:08:28,890 --> 00:08:31,290
Gao Zhiyao,
have you found someone to help?

205
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:32,770
Chief,

206
00:08:32,770 --> 00:08:35,309
the Health Division happens to have
no doctors on duty today.

207
00:08:35,309 --> 00:08:36,520
There are quite a few sick inmates.

208
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,320
So they might be too busy to help.

209
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:40,030
Tell the nurse

210
00:08:40,049 --> 00:08:41,539
that the Warden is also here.

211
00:08:41,539 --> 00:08:42,760
If you don't follow my order,

212
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,560
let's see who will be in trouble.

213
00:08:45,890 --> 00:08:47,020
Who will be in trouble?

214
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:48,270
I got an ACE!

215
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,020
You idiot.

216
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:49,770
Stop it.

217
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:50,770
