-You didn't press it, did you?

218
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:52,270
I didn't press it.

219
00:08:57,210 --> 00:08:59,460
Fine, I'll go with you.

220
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:01,640
I won't be gone for too long, I think.

221
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,020
So can you help me?

222
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:03,890
Sure.

223
00:09:03,890 --> 00:09:05,190
If he wants water later,

224
00:09:05,190 --> 00:09:07,640
please give him
some room-temperature water.

225
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:08,730
Don't let him lie down.

226
00:09:08,730 --> 00:09:10,270
Sitting or reclining is fine.

227
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,440
-Okay.
-If he coughs up phlegm,

228
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,100
check what color it is.

229
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,350
Okay.

230
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:16,640
I've already taken Inmate 7692's

231
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,390
blood pressure.

232
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:19,140
It seems a bit high now.

233
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:21,020
Please check it again in 30 minutes.

234
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:23,890
And ask Director Xiao for medical parole.

235
00:09:23,890 --> 00:09:25,390
I'll be back soon.

236
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,890
Wait for me. I'll be right back.

237
00:09:28,890 --> 00:09:30,270
It's fine.

238
00:09:30,290 --> 00:09:31,790
The Director needs you.

239
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:32,890
Seeing you,

240
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:34,770
I feel stronger than Mazinger Z.

241
00:09:34,770 --> 00:09:36,270
-Stop it.
-Go ahead.

242
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,270
Okay, bye-bye.

243
00:09:37,610 --> 00:09:39,990
-Go.
-Babe, McDonald's.

244
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:40,940
There's nothing like that here.

245
00:09:40,940 --> 00:09:42,600
Chief, we're setting off now.

246
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,640
Alright, Mazinger Z.

247
00:09:48,890 --> 00:09:50,020
Do you feel any better?

248
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:50,560
Yeah.

249
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:51,850
I'll lie down for a while.

250
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:52,440
Okay.

251
00:09:52,770 --> 00:09:54,640
Tell me right away if you feel unwell.

252
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,020
Okay, I'll let you know.

253
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:00,020
Inmate 5514, do you want some more water?

254
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,360
Hot water!

255
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,390
-Keep it down.
-I want hot water!

256
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,390
Lower your voice.

257
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:14,230
Was it a coincidence?

258
00:10:14,230 --> 00:10:15,640
Why did this happen right at this time?

259
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:17,100
Let's not worry about that now.

260
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:18,200
You've got quite a few things

261
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,530
to handle at the prison.

262
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:21,520
Otherwise, we'll hit a snag in the EIA.

263
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,980
The building contractors are waiting, too.

264
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:26,450
By the way, thank you
for your hard work, nurse.

265
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:28,140
You should all return to your posts.

266
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:29,190
-Thank you.
-Let me walk you out.

267
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:31,390
Don't bother.
I'll go to the hospital to visit him.

268
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:32,560
You stay and handle things here.

269
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,120
Okay.

270
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:35,320
Be careful on your way.

271
